an></strong></span>現場傳出歡呼聲。<br />\n<br />\n基仔再說：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好問我點解，唔好問我點解全晚都要廣東歌。太無聊嘅問題我係唔會回答。」</span></strong></span>之後再全場歡呼聲。基仔再說：「曲線都要講明。」之後即唱出《必殺技》，基仔又說：「我今晚心情好難形容！」<br />\n<br />\n早前梁詠琪紅館開個唱，都係話：「返嚟香港就梗係要講廣東話，廣東話就梗係我哋嘅母語吖嘛，今晚會盡情唱多啲廣東歌㗎。」之後即時唱了廣東歌《一天一天》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180510/58177171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58177171&d=r86lWjejdIZd%2BIgypY4vHAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=b2504dc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58177171&h=b34d589c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180510/58177171</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭 7到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"另外到場支持嘅仲有唔少前輩級，包括蘇施黃、金燕玲、汪明荃、<span style=\"color: red;\">鄺美雲</span>、陳志雲；基仔好友就有傅明憲、周慧敏和倪震夫婦、方力申、陳敏之等人，而就嚟開騷嘅張敬軒就同Mani霍汶希一齊睇。<br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲聽到古巨基咁講會唔會黑面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"汪阿蛆你都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:52:43.000Z","msg":"Hocc 都仲年年拜佢年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偽人黎姐"},{"pid":"81e18aaa6f49500069ab6189cd73dfe60e86b6ed","tid":660528,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:03:22.000Z","msg":"抽到乾哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207fa17621e99a96a905d2c2eb18b945d730a941","tid":660528,"uid":179409,"like":168,"dislike":0,"score"