ef=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180510/58177171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58177171&d=r86lWjejdIZd%2BIgypY4vHAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=b2504dc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180510%2F58177171&h=b34d589c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180510/58177171</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭 7到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"另外到場支持嘅仲有唔少前輩級，包括蘇施黃、金燕玲、汪明荃、<span style=\"color: red;\">鄺美雲</span>、陳志雲；基仔好友就有傅明憲、周慧敏和倪震夫婦、方力申、陳敏之等人，而就嚟開騷嘅張敬軒就同Mani霍汶希一齊睇。<br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲聽到古巨基咁講會唔會黑面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"汪阿蛆你都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"呀姐都係唱粵曲<br />\n用下係個閪腦估下佢撐邊邊"},{"pid":"b5bb644643eadcb15faa9a8c2e017e3fb9c59c57","tid":660528,"uid":176114,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"addcf91d3309630adfb4dddffdc716faf4d0e90e","tid":660528,"uid":85456,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"bd1680dd630f83866ec6ce22ceb4037774ee7156","tid":660528,"uid":35129,"like":217,"dislike":1,"score":216,"quote":{"pid":"e8cec1f98c56ecc949e7c2b109483d88951dd745","tid":660528,"uid":179409,"like":216,"dislike":3,"score":213,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"另外到場支持嘅仲有唔少前輩級，包括蘇施黃、金燕玲、汪明荃、<span style=\"color: red;\">鄺美雲</span>、陳志雲；基仔好友就有傅明憲、周慧敏和倪震夫婦、方力申、陳敏之等人，而就嚟開騷嘅張敬軒就同Mani霍汶希一齊睇。<br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲聽到古巨基咁講會唔會黑面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji